# Project Rules (for AI Agents)

This project is a high-performance, modern web application built with **Astro 5** and **Tailwind CSS**, deployed on **Cloudflare Workers**.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Astro 5.16+
- **Runner**: Cloudflare Pages (`@astrojs/cloudflare`)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Content**: MDX/Markdown via Content Collections
- **Infrastructure**: Cloudflare R2, KV

## Development Guidelines
- Always use **pnpm** for package management.
- Prefer **Astro Components** over UI frameworks unless interactive state is complex.
- Use the **Astro Docs MCP Server** (`https://mcp.docs.astro.build/mcp`) for up-to-date framework knowledge.
- Follow the custom integration patterns in `vendor/integration`.
- Ensure all images are optimized and served via R2 if applicable.

## File Structure
- `src/components`: UI components.
- `src/layouts`: Page layouts.
- `src/pages`: Routing.
- `src/content`: Content collections.
- `vendor/`: Custom project-specific integrations and utilities.
